ivardefs.name: source
ivardefs.desc: The name of the parameter or dot-separated path of parameter names pointing to the resource parameter that is expected to contain a reference to this resource.

ivardefs.name: sourceId
ivardefs.desc: The id of the element in the referencing resource that is expected to resolve to this resource.

properties.desc: Identifies other resource parameters within the operation invocation that are expected to resolve to this resource.
